Chicco Spring Hook On Chair (Yellow) Price: Rs.2990

Key Features

  • Entire Chair Weighs Up to 2700 g
  • Outer Cover is Made of Sturdy Techno Material
  • Measures: 25.19 x 14.17 x 14.17 inch
  • Locking Screw Allows the Hook on Chair to be Fixed

The Chicco Spring Hook-on Chair is a table seat that can be easily fixed to most desktop models with a pin that can be screwed up. This Hook On Chair from Chicco\xa0will become an easy and practical solution at home when the entire family is dining at the table and you can include your little one to dine with you at the table. The outer cover is made of sturdy techno-material and the entire chair weighs only up to 2700 g with dimensions of 640 x 360 x 360 mm.

This Spring Hook On Chair from Chicco is suitable for children between the ages 6 and 36 months. With the mounting system with locking key on the Chicco Spring Hook On Chair you can now have your little darling by your side each time you eat at the table.
